  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Education for Change - Transformative Education for Children and Youth in Ghana</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The scope will include promoting access to basic education, improving the quality of learning outcomes, and enhancing equity by promoting quality education for marginalised children, especially girls and children living in hard to reach communities.  The project scope will also include empowerment of youth to claim their rights under youth development policies and programmes. Budget analysis and advocacy will also be pursued with a view to increasing investment in education, ensuring efficiency in education spending and achieving equity in the use of education resources.</narrative>
  </description>
